{
  "stem": "21004.10",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was making $27, $27.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my uncle say, you know what, you are a good cook to my wife.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'll open up a restaurant.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He opened up a luncheonette and with refrigeration, a small luncheonette.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And not in a famous place, but a nice place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were there, making out pretty good.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then one day close to a year, Gypsies moved in, and that whole strip-- a lot of Gypsies moved in.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know from where they came.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was so much-- so much noise and so much problems.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were going begging, but the customers, customers was afraid.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I have to close that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have to close, take all the fixtures to Coney Island.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that was-- I was for three summers in Coney Island, had a beer garden.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then from there, after three summers I didn't like it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a gypsy life, living there, and only in the summer.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went to work for a firm where they make stained glass windows, so I was doing the Jewish lettering.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Before I came, they made the artists-- the main artist was a German.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a lot of Polish and American.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So when they made the Jewish lettering in the synagogues they make a little dot, like a [NON-ENGLISH] and a [NON-ENGLISH], you know, a [NON-ENGLISH], all mistakes.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You came in to put the windows in the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The rabbi comes in, he looks, this whole window has to go out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This piece has to go out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You have to take all the windows out and change all the things they make.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So when I came there, the boss gave me to work on the Jewish lettering.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I fired it also, in fire.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
